source: TEXT_CTSETCVOYAGERMOOGLE_00566_VOYAGERMOOGLE_00001<tab>Just wait until you see what I have to trade, kupo. All sorts of trinkets and baubles I'm positive you adventurer types will like... If only I could remember where I put it all.
target:
TEXT_CTSETCVOYAGERMOOGLE_00566_VOYAGERMOOGLE_00001<tab>旅から旅の生活で、モグが見つけた素敵な品を提供するクポ！
と、言いたいところだけど、ただいま準備中クポ……。
